\begin{bmatrix}1&2&3\\ 2&3&1\\ 3&1&2\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}1&0&0\\ 2&1&0\\ 3&5&1\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}1&2&3\\ 0&-1&-5\\ 0&0&18\end{bmatrix}. \url{http://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2.E6} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;}
\mathbf{A}=\begin{bmatrix}b_{1}&c_{1}&&&0\\ a_{2}&b_{2}&c_{2}&&\\ &\ddots&\ddots&\ddots&\\ &&a_{n-1}&b_{n-1}&c_{n-1}\\ 0&&&a_{n}&b_{n}\end{bmatrix}. \url{http://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2.E7} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;}
\mathbf{L}=\begin{bmatrix}1&0&&&0\\ \ell_{2}&1&0&&\\ &\ddots&\ddots&\ddots&\\ &&\ell_{n-1}&1&0\\ 0&&&\ell_{n}&1\end{bmatrix}, \url{http://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2.E8} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;} \symbolDefined[\ell_{jk}]{C3.S2.XMD2.m1bdec}
\mathbf{U}=\begin{bmatrix}d_{1}&u_{1}&&&0\\ 0&d_{2}&u_{2}&&\\ &\ddots&\ddots&\ddots&\\ &&0&d_{n-1}&u_{n-1}\\ 0&&&0&d_{n}\end{bmatrix}, \url{http://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2.E9} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;} \symbolDefined[u_{j}]{C3.S2.XMD4.m1bdec} \symbolUsed[d_{j}]{C3.S2.XMD5.m1bdec}
\ell_{j}=a_{j}/d_{j-1}, \url{https://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2#Ex1} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;} \symbolDefined[d_{j}]{C3.S2.XMD5.m1badec} \symbolUsed[\ell_{jk}]{C3.S2.XMD2.m1badec}

\|\mathbf{x}\|_{p}=\left(\sum_{j=1}^{n}\abs{x_{j}}^{p}\right)^{1/p}, \url{https://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2#Ex3} \constraint{p=1,2,\dots}
\|\mathbf{x}\|_{\infty}=\max_{1\leq j\leq n}\abs{x_{j}}. \url{https://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2#Ex4}
\|\mathbf{A}\|_{p}=\max_{\mathbf{x}\neq\boldsymbol{{0}}}\frac{\|\mathbf{A}\mathbf{x}\|_{p}}{\|\mathbf{x}\|_{p}}\,. \url{http://dlmf.nist.gov/3.2.E14} \comments{Warning: Falling back to standard tex;}
